## Attribution Requirements

When using this automation template in your projects:

1. **Required**: Include this license file in your project root
2. **Recommended**: Add attribution in your README.md:
   ```markdown
   This project uses the AshTrail Development Automation Template, licensed under MIT.
   ```
3. **Optional**: Link back to the original template repository

